{"id":619077,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】药水哥直播连线到习近平儿子/","date":"2019-10-04T06:49:48Z","modified":"2019-10-04T11:51:21Z","title":"【立此存照】“药水哥”直播连线到“习近平儿子”遭全网封杀","content":"<p>[slider]9月25日，网络红人“药水哥”刘波（以骂人、假哭、说胡话等行为艺术方式吸引“黑粉”而出名）在直播连线时与网友互怼，当他质问对方“你谁呀”时，对方脱口而出一句“我是习近平他儿子”（玩笑自称）&#8230;..“药水哥”听罢露出惊恐表情并立马切断了直播。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"9.25药水哥连麦连到习近平儿子被封\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9IGkEcI6BR0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>因触碰到“超级敏感词”，之后“药水哥”多个直播平台被关闭， 经中国数字时代编辑检索发现，B站、百度贴吧已经无法查到“药水哥”的相关搜索结果，疑似享受了“全网封杀”待遇。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619079\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥.jpg 1319w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥-300x215.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥-768x550.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥-1024x733.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥-1080x773.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619080\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"196\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥2.jpg 992w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥2-300x118.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥2-768x301.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>“药水哥”的新浪微博账号仍在，但所有微博均被关闭了评论。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619081\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥3.jpg 776w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥3-300x279.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/药水哥3-768x714.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/question/8940\">品葱网友</a>恶搞图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619078\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"289\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg.jpg 1575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg-300x158.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg-768x404.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg-1024x539.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/NPeDivg-1080x568.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/%e9%9b%b7%e6%96%af%e6%9e%97-%e6%af%94%e5%92%aa%e8%92%99%e6%9b%b4%e5%8f%af%e6%80%95%e7%9a%84%ef%bc%8c%e6%98%af%e6%8c%96%e7%a5%96%e5%9d%9f%e5%bc%8f%e4%b8%be%e6%8a%a5%e6%b8%85%e7%ae%97/\">雷斯林 | 比咪蒙更可怕的，是挖祖坟式举报清算</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%97%a5%e6%8a%a5-%e4%bd%a0%e4%b8%8d%e7%88%b1%e5%9b%bd%e7%9a%84%e6%a0%b7%e5%ad%90-%e7%9c%9f%e4%b8%91%ef%bc%81/\">【异闻观止】人民日报 | 你不爱国的样子 真丑！</a></p></blockquote>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38895,38920],"tags":[13222,39014,39016,9241,39015,39013]}